{"tid":1912170,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"譚德塞讚揚習近平及特朗普領導打擊疫情　做法富有成效","createTime":"2020-03-06T00:57:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T02:13:22.000Z","uid":227628,"like":5,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"dc20602552a3a027fca5b78fb865610d489b551c","tid":1912170,"uid":227628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T00:57:53.000Z","msg":"世界衞生組織總幹事譚德塞表示，現時新型冠狀病毒肺炎的疫情，仍未去到全球大流行的地步，但已經出現令人憂慮的跡象。<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞批評部分國家在疫情威脅之下，未有表現出足夠的政治承諾水平，一些國家只是將應對疫情的工作，下放給衛生部門處理，而不是全國一同應對，他稱讚中國及美國，分別由國家主席習近平、總統特朗普及副總統彭斯領導整個政府應對疫情的做法有成效，呼籲每個國家採取快速、大規模及果斷的行動控制疫情。<br />\n<br />\n另外，世衞官員回應香港有狗隻驗出對新型冠狀病毒有弱陽性，認為未有證據證明病毒出現人傳狗或狗傳人的情況，但會與港府密切聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1512771-20200306.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1512771-20200306.htm&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcMg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=fa112c2d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1512771-20200306.htm&h=4837ab4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1512771-20200306.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n買兩邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5345eb94e07d5ba7ea9f29e2deab3d3e7cb996b7","tid":1912170,"uid":21545,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T00:58:47.000Z","msg":"而家先奶美國 too late<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a642ed7df21a0d66fc65ebb8a6ba6b95eb0751f","tid":1912170,"uid":28279,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T00:59:31.000Z","msg":"靠擦鞋拎經費<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死乞衣"},{"pid":"06d5e2ba3b5b320d6beea01bce2a217a9a6cd3a1","tid":1912170,"uid":53003,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T01:00:08.000Z","msg":"唔係買兩邊，係拉埋美國落水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞分化<img src=\"/as